    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The user looks at the mirror and try to recall any information, talking with himself against the mirror. The user can make any Knowledge check (even untrained), and receives +1 insight bonus for the duration of technique.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Requires:</b> Mirror Arts (f)</p>\n<p><b>Material Focus:</b> One Mirror.</p>\n<p><b>Empower:</b> The user may spend 1 point of chakra to increase the bonus by +2, up to +2 per level or +10.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Every step of mastery in this technique lets the user re-roll a Knowledge Check per day with Insight Bonus, up to 5/day.</p>\n",
